3EThe%20trouble%20with%20soft%20skills%20is%20we%20all%20think%20we've%20got%20'em.%20But%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZW8zvaTRuGo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECarrie%20Fisher%20pointed%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Harry%20Met%20Sally%2C%26quot%3B%20everybody%20thinks%20they%20have%20good%20taste%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20humor%20but%20they%20couldn't%20possibly%20all%20have%20such%20things.%20So%20some%20of%20us%20will%20have%20to%20bone%20up.%20How%20you%20write%20that%20email%2C%20how%20you%20participate%20in%20a%20meeting%2C%20or%20how%20you%20handle%20that%20jerk%20of%20a%20client%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-want-more-training-hard-skills-survey-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ematter%20more%20than%20how%20well%20you%20code%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20pull%20together%20a%20slide%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20developing%20is%20a%20whole%20generation%20of%20people%20who%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20soft%20skills%20mean%20because%20they%20assume%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20about%20the%20tools%20that%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Norman%20Bacal%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BTake%20Charge%3A%20The%20Skills%20That%20Drive%20Professional%20Success%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Insider%20in%20reference%20to%20communication%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20we%20can%20sharpen%20our%20soft%20skills%2C%20Bacal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20the%20bosses%20seem%20to%20want.%20Management%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20customer%20service%20are%20the%20top%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D369721933a2f14ee1a522fdf7fddb7192c34b06e88af388e06fb5dd60c009c24%26postID%3D653bf74dd5adb6e8ec7f0a33%26postSlug%3Demployers-want-soft-skills-good-communication-teamwork-leadership-energetic-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fbusiness%252Ftalent%252Fblog%252Ftalent-strategy%252Flinkedin-most-in-demand-hard-and-soft-skills%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ein-demand%20job%20skills%20for%202023%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20LinkedIn.%20The%20job-search%20engine%20Adzuna%20recently%20reviewed%20ads%20for%20jobs%20paying%20over%20%24200K%20and%C2%A0found%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adzuna.com%2Fblog%2Fthe-soft-skills-top-earners-in-the-us-have-in-common%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo.%201%20soft%20skill%3C%2Fa%3E%20employers%20were%20looking%20for%20was%20someone%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Benergetic.%26quot%3B%20Take%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-quiet-quitting-work-ethic-millennials-money-struggles-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Equiet%20quitting%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Neave%2C%20head%20of%20data%20science%20at%20Adzuna%2C%20compares%20soft%20skills%20to%20people%20skills.%20He%20told%20Insider%20employers%20are%20looking%20closer%20at%20job%20candidates'%20abilities%20around%20the%20squishy%20stuff.%20Being%20strong%20in%20areas%20like%20communication%2C%20leadership%2C%20and%20teamwork%20can%20be%20linked%20to%20longevity%20in%20a%20job%2C%20greater%20potential%20for%20moving%20into%20management%2C%20and%20an%20ability%20to%20build%20relationships.%20Employers%20also%20see%20these%20attributes%20as%20indicators%20people%20will%20stay%20more%20tied%20into%20what%20they%20do%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20slight%20reaction%20against%20disengagement%20that%20I%20think%20some%20employers%20have%20felt%20from%20their%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20Neave%20said%20of%20the%20focus%20on%20soft%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20will%20mean%20we%20have%20to%20get%20better%20at%20this%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Selker%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20North%20American%20technology%20practice%20leader%20at%20the%20executive%20search%20firm%20Stanton%20Chase%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20employers%20increasingly%20realize%20that%20they%20have%20to%20consider%20more%20than%20just%20whether%20a%20worker%20delivers%20on%20a%20task.%20%26quot%3BYou%20also%20have%20to%20then%20look%20at%20how%20this%20person%20gets%20their%20job%20done%2C%20not%20just%20the%20results%20that%20they%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20leads%20directly%20into%20these%20areas%20of%20the%20so-called%20soft%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelker%20said%20that%20because%20soft%20skills%20can%20be%20observed%2C%20they%20can%20be%20measured%2C%20even%20if%20somewhat%20subjectively.%20But%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20employers%20train%20key%20workers%20on%20assessing%20soft%20skills%2C%20the%20evaluations%20can%20become%20more%20concrete.%20Measuring%20soft%20skills%20can%20then%20become%20more%20like%20evaluating%20hard%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20is%20a%20shift%20in%20thinking%20then%20to%20say%2C%20'Can%20we%20observe%20these%20soft%20skills%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20answer%20is%20yes%2C%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelker%20said%20as%20automation%20takes%20on%20bigger%20roles%20in%20many%20jobs%2C%20the%20gigs%20many%20of%20us%20have%20will%20shift%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20things%20like%20strategy.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20in%20those%20jobs%20will%20have%20a%20higher%20bar%20that%20will%20need%20to%20be%20met%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20ability%20to%20achieve%20those%20softer%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraining%20can%20help%20us%20improve%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERen%C3%A9e%20Pizzarello%2C%20who%20is%20a%20recruiter%20for%20senior-%20and%20manager-level%20jobs%20in%20accounting%20and%20finance%2C%20told%20Insider%20many%20employers%20are%20stepping%20up%20their%20focus%20on%20soft%20skills%20because%20so%20many%20of%20us%20have%20become%20bad%20at%20basics%20like%20communication.%20It's%20happened%20as%20our%20informal%20social%20media%20and%20texting%20habits%20have%20followed%20us%20to%20our%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20where%20you%20are%20at%20work.%20People%20write%20a%20lazy%20message%20to%20you%20all%20the%20time.%20It%20isn't%20like%20a%20constructed%20'I'm%20gonna%20think%20through%20what%20I%20need%20to%20say.'%20People%20literally%20have%20no%20filter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20is%20a%20breakdown%20in%20communication.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20plug%20potential%20gaps%20in%20workers'%20skills%2C%20some%20employers%20are%20rolling%20out%20how%20to's%20on%20the%20particulars%20of%20interacting%20with%20others.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-complaining-millennials-gen-x-should-listen-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EKPMG%20conducts%20training%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20for%20younger%20workers.%20The%20pandemic%20meant%20that%20many%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20as%20they%20started%20their%20careers%2C%20didn't%20get%20the%20face-to-face%20interactions%20at%20work%20that%20might%20have%20allowed%20them%20to%20further%20develop%20their%20soft%20skills.%20KPMG's%20lessons%20cover%20topics%20like%20how%20to%20present%20to%20clients%2C%20what%20background%20you%20should%20have%20on%20video%20calls%2C%20and%20how%20to%20write%20a%20professional%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeave%2C%20from%20Adzuna%2C%20said%20workers%20who%20can%20demonstrate%20to%20their%20bosses%20and%20potential%20employers%20that%20they%20can%20conduct%20themselves%20well%20will%20have%20an%20advantage%20as%20tech%20like%20AI%20marches%20deeper%20into%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20these%20types%20of%20soft%20skills%2C%20not%20only%20are%20you%20kind%20of%20more%20employable%20right%20now%2C%20but%20you're%20almost%20like%20future-proofing%20your%20employability%20for%20the%20next%20five%2C%2010%20years%20when%20things%20are%20really%20go