0rental%20when%20he%20vacationed%20there.%3Cp%3ELorenzo%20Di%20Cola%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EYou're%20never%20going%20to%20need%20a%20charging%20station%20unless%20you're%20on%20a%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20put%20a%20charger%20in%20your%20garage%20and%20you're%20going%20to%20wake%20up%20every%20morning%20with%20300%2C%20280%2C%20250%2C%20however%20many%20miles%2C%20and%20virtually%20nobody%20drives%20that%20much%20in%20a%20day.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20there%20are%20Superchargers%2C%20etcetera%2C%20all%20around%20you.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20say%2C%20'What%20about%20trips%3F'%20I%20ask%20where%20they%20go%2C%20and%20here%20in%20Utah%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20locations.%20If%20you%20leave%20with%20a%20full%20charge%2C%20you'll%20stop%20at%20one%20of%20the%20Superchargers%20between%20here%20and%20there%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20two%20minutes%20like%20gas%2C%20but%20you'll%20get%20a%20drink%2C%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20check%20your%20phone%2C%20and%20you're%20out%20of%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20variety%20of%20EVs%20are%20popular%20with%20buyers%2C%20but%20especially%20Teslas%20given%20their%20market%20share%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20Teslas%2C%20Model%20Ys%20and%20Model%203s%2C%20plus%20Rivians%20are%20really%20popular.%20We've%20had%20some%20good%20luck%20with%20the%20Ford%20Lightnings.%20We're%20starting%20to%20see%20certain%20Audis%2C%20and%20BMWs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20as%20much%20the%20Hyundais%2C%20Kias%2C%20Mach-Es%2C%20or%20Chevrolet%20Bolts.%20I%20think%20those%20are%20going%20to%20become%20more%20popular%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-electric-vehicle-january-for-better-tax-credits-but-caveats-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20tax%20changes%20happening%20in%20January%2C%20where%20you%20can%20use%20the%20credit%20as%20a%20down%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20will%20make%