cently%2C%20like%20many%20Brits%2C%20I%20had%20never%20set%20foot%20in%20a%20Costco.%20The%20discount%20retailer%20currently%20has%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.costco.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2023%2FCostco-Wholesale-Corporation-Reports-September-Sales-Results%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E29%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20compared%20to%20591%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20107%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20parents%20weren't%20members%2C%20and%20because%20I%20don't%20own%20a%20car%20it%20never%20made%20sense%20for%20me%20to%20join%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20I%20finally%20went%20to%20a%20Costco%20store.%20Here's%20what%20surprised%20me%20from%20my%20first%20visit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Staff%20check%20your%20cards%20by%20the%20door%20and%20you%20have%20to%20show%20your%20receipts%20and%20purchases%20on%20the%20way%20out%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Entrance%20to%20Costco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653902210487ff031cadad25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222076%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaff%20checked%20customers'%20membership%20cards%20on%20their%20way%20into%20the%20store.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20Costco%20had%20recently%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-cracking-down-on-card-sharing-at-self-checkout-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emembership%20crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20seemed%20surprising%20that%20the%20store%20has%20employees%20staff%20the%20entrance%20and%20check%20membership%20cards%20when%20customers%20have%20to%20flash%20their%20cards%20at%20the%20checkouts%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20exit%20the%20store%2C%20you%20also%20had%20to%20show%20a%20member%20of%20staff%20your%20receipt%20and%20purchases%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20seemed%20quite%20labor-intensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20It%20was%20really%20busy%20for%20a%20Friday%20afternoon%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customers%20at%20the%20checkouts%20of%20a%20Costco%20store%20in%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6537d10896f7540cd063c4cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20hadn't%20expected%20the%20store%20to%20be%20so%20busy.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20arrived%20shortly%20after%202%20p.m.%20on%20a%20Friday%2C%20and%20the%20store%20was%20much%20busier%20than%20I'd%20thought.%20The%20customers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-memberships-young-people-age-gen-z-x-boomer-jelinek-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espanned%20a%20range%20of%20ages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too%2C%20whereas%20I'd%20expected%20them%20to%20be%20mainly%20retirees%20at%20that%20time%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Items%20were%20sold%20in%20giant%20packs%20or%20as%20smaller%20packs%20bundled%20together%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nescaf%C3%A9%20Azera%20Americano%20coffee%20tins%3B%20Grace%20Dean%20holding%20up%20a%205kg%20block%20of%20cheese%20in%20Costco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65365fbe96908fd7cdb4f6d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20wowed%20by%20the%20five-kilogram%20(11-pound)%20blocks%20of%20cheese.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20items%2C%20as%20I'd%20expected%2C%20were%20sold%20in%20massive%20sizes.%20This%20included%20five-kilogram%20(11-pound)%20blocks%20of%20cheese%20costing%20around%20%C2%A325%20(about%20%2430)%2C%20huge%20bottles%20of%20fabric%20conditioner%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20last%20250%20washes%20each%2C%20and%20even%2025-kilogram%20(55-pound)%20packs%20of%20sugar%20that%20I%20had%20no%20hopes%20of%20lifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20products%20were%20in%20large%20multipacks%2C%20too%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20a%20pack%20of%201%2C100%20tea%20bags%20and%20a%20box%20containing%2048%20bags%20of%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20how%20many%20products%20were%20actually%20made%20of%20individual%20packs%20bundled%20and%20sold%20together.%20I%20noticed%20this%20with%20jars%20of%20pesto%2C%20boxes%20of%20cereal%2C%20and%20packs%20of%20mac%20and%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20I%20saw%20more%20American%20brands%20than%20I%20expected%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jars%20of%20Smucker's%20Goober%20stocked%20at%20Costco%3B%20packs%20of%20Angie's%20Boomchickapop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653666dc96f7540cd062d337%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20saw%20American%20products%20I'd%20never%20spotted%20at%20other%20UK%20grocery%20chains%20before.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-food-aisles-uk-grocers-supermarkets-tesco-sainsburys-store-shop-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20brands%20and%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20aren't%20commonly%20available%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20products%20like%20Oreos%2C%20Nerds%2C%20and%20Ben%20%26amp%3B%20Jerry's%20are%20widely%20sold%20over%20here%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20find%20Kraft%20Macaroni%20and%20Cheese%2C%20Skippy%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20Cheetos%2C%20for%20example.%20But%20Costco%20sold%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20even%20some%20more%20niche%20products%2C%20like%20Smucker's%20Goober%20spread%2C%20Red%20Vines%20licorice%2C%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Coffee%2C%20and%20Mike%20and