064%20packs.%3Cp%3EWill%20Martin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20I'd%20ever%20seen%20stamps%20for%20sale%20like%20this%20before.%20Previously%2C%20I've%20only%20ever%20bought%20them%20from%20the%20Post%20Office%2C%20where%20a%20staff%20member%20retrieves%20them%20for%20you%20from%20behind%20the%20counter%2C%20or%20from%20customer%20service%20desks%20in%20grocery%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20other%20products%20on%20sale%2C%20Costco%20sold%20the%20stamps%20in%20large%20packs.%20I%20saw%2064%20first-class%20stamps%20for%20%C2%A376.99%20(%2493)%2C%20or%2064%20second-class%20stamps%20for%20%C2%A347.19%20(%2457)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20slight%20discount%20from%20buying%20them%20at%20other%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E7.%20My%20illusions%20about%20a%20cake%20sold%20at%20my%20local%20caf%C3%A9%20were%20shattered%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cakes%20on%20sale%20at%20Costco%2C%20including%20a%20carrot%20cake%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653905810487ff031cadae0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECostco%20sold%20this%20whopping%20carrot%20cake%20that%20weighed%20in%20at%20nearly%20five%20pounds.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%C2%A32.50%20(just%20over%20%243)%2C%20my%20local%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20my%20hometown%20sold%20an%20incredible%20carrot%20cake.%20Deliciously%20moist%2C%20it%20was%20packed%20with%20nuts%2C%20topped%20with%20a%20rich%20cream%20cheese%20frosting%2C%20and%20decorated%20with%20charming%20iced%20carrots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20visit%2C%20I%20told%20a%20member%20of%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20about%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20cake%2C%20to%20which%20they%20responded%20that%20they%20bought%20it%20from%20elsewhere.%20I%20wondered%20if%20perhaps%20they%20got%20it%20from%20a%20local%20bakery%2C%20but%20when%20I%20visited%20Costco%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20retailer%20sold%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20the%20same%20cake%20%E2%80%93%20then%20a%20near-exact%20replica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20sold%20a%20large%20assortment%20of%20large%20cakes%2C%20multi-packs%20of%20pastries%20and%20bread%20rolls%2C%20and%20other%20baked%20goods%2C%20and%20I%20wondered%20how%20many%20other%20caf%C3%A9s%20they%20supplied.%20The%20coveted%20carrot%20cake%20cost%20%C2%A311.49%20(%2414)%20and%20had%20a%20minimum%20weight%20of%202.2%20kilograms%20(nearly%20five%20pounds).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E8.%20I%20hadn't%20expected%20quite%20so%20many%20luxury%20and%20big-ticket%20items%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bikes%20and%20jewelry%20on%20sale%20at%20a%20Costco%20in%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538f3c3356802a56be3253b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20jewelry%20on%20sale%20cost%20more%20than%20%C2%A31%2C000%20(%241%2C200).%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20sold%20a%20massive%20range%20of%20low-priced%20essentials%2C%20and%20large%20areas%20of%20the%20store%20were%20dedicated%20to%20baked%20goods%2C%20meat%2C%20alcohol%2C%20cleaning%20supplies%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20there%20were%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-shoppers-cut-back-big-ticket-items-spend-appliances-electrics-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20and%20big-ticket%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20I'd%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20a%20selection%20of%20bicycles%2C%20Xbox%20consoles%2C%20a%20telescope%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20expensive%20jewelry%20and%20watches.%20Some%20of%20the%20ovens%20and%20watches%20I%20saw%20cost%20more%20than%20%C2%A32%2C000%20(%242%2C400).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9.%20The%20store%20was%20difficult%20to%20navigate%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20aisles%20in%20a%20Costco%20store%20in%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538f94f96f7540cd064f68a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20aisles%2C%20though%20numbered%2C%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20labelled%20with%20the%20type%20of%20goods%20they%20contained.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20products%20were%20generally%20sorted%20into%20categories%2C%20there%20wasn't%20a%20clear%20distinction%20between%20the%20food%20and%20general%20merchandise%20parts%20of%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aisles%2C%20though%20numbered%2C%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20labeled%20with%20the%20type%20of%20goods%20they%20contained%2C%20which%20is%20something%20I'm%20used%20to%20seeing%20in%20large%20stores.%20I%20can%20imagine%20it%20would%20take%20a%20while%20to%20learn%20your%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E10.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20store%20was%20pretty%20tidy%20overall%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aisle%20of%20produce%20in%20a%20Costco%20store%20with%20some%20shoppers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539006b356802a56be32e03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20wasn't%20much%20clutter.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20seemed%20pretty%20clean%20and%20tidy%20to%20me.%20There%20were%20quite%20a%20few%20bins%20dotted%20about%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20customers%20to%20bin%20the%20cups%20or%20cocktail%20sticks%20their%20free%20samples%20were%20served%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aisles%20were%20really%20wide%2C%20too%2C%20making%20them%20easy%20to%20walk%20around%20with%20big%20shopping%20carts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20at%20German%20discount%20retailers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faldis-us-popularity-middle-income-inflation-cheap-prices-costs-stores-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAldi%20and%20Lidl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Costco%20displayed%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20products%20straight%20in%20the%20boxes%20they%20were%20delivered%20in.%20This%20allows%20the%20warehouse%20chain%20to%20save%20money%20on%20labor%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E11.%20The%20food%20court%20was%20crazily%20cheap%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Costco%20food%20court%20with%20menu%2C%20cooks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6537d6d30487ff031cac8e32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20in%20the%20food%20court%20was%20ridiculously%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%C2%A31.99%20(about%20%242.40)%20for%20a%20massive%20slice%20of%20five-cheese%20pizza%2C%20which%20was%20very%20greasy%20but%20certainly%20filled%20me%20up.%20There%20were%20three%20flavors%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20and%20for%20%C2%A39.99%20(just%20over%20%2412)%20you%20could%20buy%20a%20whole%2018-inch%20pizza.%20I%20also%20got%20unlimited%20Pepsico%20soda%20refills%20for%20%C2%A31.19%20(%241.45).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Costco%20also%20sold%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostcos-iconic-hot-dog-still-150-despite-record-inflation-rates-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20dog%20and%20soda%20bundle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20just%20%C2%A31.50%20(%241.82).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20expected%20the%20food%20court%20to%20be%20cheap%2C%20but%20not%20quite%20this%20cheap.%20Despite%20Costco%20hiking%20up%20some%20of%20the%20UK%20food-court%20prices%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-hot-dogs-best-items-food-court-comparison-review-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20Insider%20reporters%20reviewed%20the%20offerings%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20the%20prices%20were%20still%20incredibly%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20dining%20area%20was%20nothing%20fancy%2C%20the%20tables%20seemed%20clean%20and%20there%20was%20a%20vending%20machine%20selling%20bottles%20of%20water%20for%20around%2030%20cents%20as%20well%20as%20free%20ketchup%20and%20mayo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E12.%20You%20can%20book%20vacations%20and%20get%20your%20tires%20replaced%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223680%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20optician%20section%20of%20a%20Costco%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6537dcaf96f7540cd063dec6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20could%20even%20get%20your%20eyes%20tested%20and%20buy%20glasses%20and%20contact%20lenses.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20Costco%20in%20the%20US%20offered%20a%20ton%20of%20extra%20services%20to%20its%20customers%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20that%20the%20UK%20business%20did%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20a%20tire%20center%20selling%20tires%20and%20offering%20puncture%20repair%20services.%20A%20large%20leaflet%20stand%20near%20the%20door%20as%20you%20exited%20the%20store%20offered%20information%20on%20%26quot%3BCostco%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20included%20vacations%2C%20air-conditioning%20installation%2C%20and%20Hertz%20rental-van%20hire.%20Signs%20in%20the%20deli%20offered%20click-and-collect%20entertaining%20platters%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20even%20get%20your%20eyes%20tested%20and%20buy%20glasses%20and%20contact%20lenses%2C%20which%20goes%20for%20all%20of%20Costco's%20stores%20in%20the%20UK.%20Some%20UK%20Costco%20stores%20have%20hearing-aid%20centers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.costco.co.uk%2Fstore-finder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egas%20stations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-first-timer-review-most-surprising-things-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698572907000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653e283f356802a56be6dc84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-first-timer-review-most-surprising-things-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20impressed%20by%20Costco's%20tidiness%2C%20food%20court%2C%20and%20vast%20range%20of%20goods%2C%20but%20the%20free%20product%20samples%20were%20tiny%20and%20the%20store%20was%20hard%20to%20navigate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-first-timer-review-most-surprising-things-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20fleeing%20Florida%20after%20almost%2040%20years%20because%20'Rolls%20Royces%2C%20Range%20Rovers%20and%20Maseratis%20took%20over'%20and%20my%20home%20insurance%20skyrocketed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22palm%20beac%20shore%20florida%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653c12810487ff031cb1075a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Bolin%20Photography%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDavid%2C%2058%2C%20had%20loved%20the%20slow%20pace%20and%20friendly%20community%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20since%201987.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20home%20insurance%20costs%20and%20property%20taxes%20rose%2C%20making%20life%20less%20affordable%20as%20retirement%20loomed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThen%20newcomers%20moved%20in%20with%20flashy%20cars%20and%20bad%20attitudes.%20So%20David%20is%20moving%20to%20Georgia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20David%2C%2058%2C%20who%20is%20moving%20to%20Savannah%2C%20Georgia%2C%20next%20year%20after%20almost%2040%20years%20living%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%20He%20asked%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20his%20first%20name%20for%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20but%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20identity.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20from%20a%20small%20Midwestern%20town%20outside%20of%20Chicago%2C%20and%20as%20a%20child%20I%20dreamed%20of%20moving%20to%20Florida.%20My%20grandparents%20were%20snowbirds.%20We%20would%20drive%20down%20to%20see%20them%2C%20and%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20held%20some%20mystique%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20graduated%20college%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20not%20start%20my%20adult%20life%20there%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20loaded%20up%20the%20car%2C%20and%20I%20landed%20on%20Halloween%20of%201987.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20maybe%2080%2C000%20people%20lived%20in%20West%20Palm.%20Many%20people%20knew%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20cultural%20and%20financial%20shift%20in%20Florida.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%2058%20now.%20I%20started%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20I%20get%20older%2C%20do%20I%20really%20want%20to%20be%20here%3F%20I%20didn't%20see%20the%20bright%20side%20of%20staying.%26quot%3B%20So%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20sold%20our%20house%20at%20a%20massive%20profit%20and%20bought%20one%20in%20Savannah%2C%20Georgia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20spent%20nearly%2040%20years%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20came%20to%20West%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20I%20moved%20into%20this%20great%20little%20area%20that%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with.%20I%20lived%20in%20a%20condo%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20then%20I%20bought%20property%20for%20%24150%2C000%20back%20in%201989%20or%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20great%20property%20on%20a%20huge%20lot.%20During%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%20I%20took%20a%20risk%20and%20planned%20to%20add%20onto%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20brother-in-law%2C%20who%20is%20a%20contractor%2C%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20get%20great%20prices%20for%20everything%20because%20we're%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20housing%20crisis.%20Everything%20from%20concrete%20to%20your%20roof%20to%20appliances%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20it%20at%20a%20reasonable%20price%20and%20quickly.%26quot%3B%20We%20got%20a%20%24700%2C000%20construction%20loan%2C%20and%20it%20worked%20out%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David's%20three%20dogs%20in%20his%20old%20neighborhood%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653c135196f7540cd0684725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid's%20three%20dogs%20in%20his%20old%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20neighborhood%2C%20everyone%20knew%20each%20other.%20We%20were%20really%20tight-knit%20and%20very%20neighborly.%C2%A0%20Many%20of%20us%20would%20walk%20dogs%2C%20stop%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20and%20chit-chat.%20We%20used%20to%20do%20a%20Secret%20Santa%20gifting%2C%20where%20at%203%20a.m.%20Christmas%20morning%2C%20we'd%20leave%20wine%20on%2030%20of%20our%20neighbors'%20front%20porches.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENewcomers%20with%20Rolls%20Royces%20and%20Maseratis%20flooded%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20neighborhood%20changed%20dramatically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20people%20who%20were%20moving%20down%20and%20spending%20crazy%20amounts%20of%20money%20was%20insane.%20Their%20attitudes%20were%20so%20different%20from%20what%20everybody%20was%20used%20to.%20These%20were%20demanding%20people%2C%20not%20familiar%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20calm%20lifestyle.%20The%20population%20doubled%20with%20people%20different%20from%20others%20in%20our%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20people%20who%20moved%20in%20were%20in%20finance.%20Many%20had%20family%20money.%20They%20were%20just%20throwing%20money%20out%20there%20like%20it%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eno%20big%20deal.%20Like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20sold%20my%20apartment%20in%20New%20York%20for%20%244%20million%20and%20I%20bought%20this%20for%20%242%20million.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERolls%20Royces%2C%20Range%20Rovers%20and%20Maseratis%20took%20over%20the%20area%20with%20disregard%20for%20rules%20of%20the%20road.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20to%20walk%20with%20our%20neighbors%2C%20their%20kids%2C%20and%20our%20dogs.%20Then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20these%20cars%20are%20speeding%20through.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20short%20block%20and%20the%20speed%20limit%20is%20clearly%2025%20miles%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20they%20were%20getting%20up%20to%2060%20miles%20an%20hour.%20They're%20whipping%20around%20these%20curbs%20and%20we're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20hell%20is%20going%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20would%20try%20to%20put%20an%20orange%20cone%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20to%20stop%20this%20behavior.%20People%20became%20more%20hesitant%20to%20hang%20out%20on%20walks.%20There%20was%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20disrespect%20for%20the%20community%20in%20that%20way.%20I%20hear%20from%20our%20friends%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20that%20it%20still%20goes%20on%20and%20that%20it's%20worse.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20residents%20added%20privacy%20hedges%20and%20fences%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20bubble.%20They%20started%20creating%20these%20cocoons.%20They%20started%20building%20walls%20and%20didn't%20engage%20with%20anybody%20in%20the%20neighborhood.%C2%A0I'm%20not%20saying%20it's%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20so%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHome%20insurance%20premiums%20and%20property%20taxes%20skyrocketed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHomeowners%20insurance%20really%20started%20climbing%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftimeline-of-miami-building-collapse-reveals-prior-warnings-details-dates-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Surfside%20condo%20building%20collapsed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20I%20paid%20about%20%247%2C000%20per%20year%20in%20homeowners%20insurance.%20The%20woman%20who%20bought%20my%20house%20paid%20%2422%2C000%20this%20year.%C2%A0Insurance%20goes%20up%2030%25%20to%2040%25%20per%20year%2C%20and%20there's%20nothing%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20who%20bought%20my%20house%20also%20pays%20%2440%2C000%20in%20property%20taxes%20per%20year.%20Because%20of%20Florida's%20homestead%20exemption%2C%20which%20caps%20the%20amount%20an%20existing%20homeowner's%20property%20taxes%20can%20increase%20per%20year%20by%205%25%2C%20I%20only%20paid%20%2415%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20still%20a%20huge%20sum%20of%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20thinking%20about%20retirement.%20How%20was%20I%20going%20to%20pay%20these%20skyrocketing%20prices%20on%20a%20fixed%20income%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20talk%20to%20many%20retirees%20who%20are%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20gotta%20leave%20because%20I'm%20on%20a%20fixed%20income%2C%20and%20I%20can't%20afford%20these%20property%20taxes.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20sold%20my%20Florida%20house%20for%20much%20more%20than%20I%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20and%20bought%20a%20cheaper%20one%20in%20Georgia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222450%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wilmington%20Island%2C%20Florida%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653c14ae356802a56be67b86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221838%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWilmington%20Island%2C%20Florida%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Propst%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20we%20sold%20the%20house%20in%202022%20for%20%242.6%20million%2C%