ion%20Project%20Division%2C%20Bodeli%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajput%20also%20forged%20documents%2C%20signatures%20and%20other%20documents%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20government%20official.%20He%20acquired%2093%20government%20projects%20and%20received%20funds%20accumulating%20over%20Rs%204.15%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20was%20registered%20by%20Javed%20Maknojiya%2C%20working%20as%20a%20junior%20clerk%20in%20the%20administrative%20office%20of%20the%20district%20collectorate.%20As%20per%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20district%20collector%20(DC)%20Sachin%20Kumar%20convened%20a%20meeting%20on%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20applications%20requesting%20for%20Rs%203.78%20crores%20for%2012%20border%20village%20and%20lift%20irrigation%20projects%20were%20discussed%2C%20when%20officials%20realised%20that%20no%20office%20of%20the%20executive%20engineer%20existed%20in%20Bodeli.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20investigation%20was%20launched%2C%20the%20DC%20sought%20details%20of%20the%20projects%20run%20by%20the%20Bodeli%20%E2%80%98office%E2%80%99%20and%20found%20that%20Rajput%20had%20received%20Rs%204.15%20crores%20since%202021%2C%20after%20which%20he%20and%20his%20associate%20Abu%20Bakr%20Saiyed%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20witnessed%20several%20fraud%20cases%20where%20the%20accused%20impersonate%20government%20officials%20including%20those%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(CMO).%20One%20of%20these%20cases%20involved%20conman%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20top%20director%20handling%20strategies%20and%20campaigns%20in%20the%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Ahmedabad%20City%20Detection%20of%20Crime%20Branch%20(DCB)%20in%20April%20after%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20took%20his%20custody%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20police%20ar