2Fjames-michael-tyler-actor-who-played-gunther-on-friends-dies%2Fa-59613656%5C%22%3E90%E2%80%99s%20TV%20sitcom%20that%20followed%20the%20lives%20of%C2%A0six%20single%20New%20Yorkers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0navigating%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20episode%20of%20%3Cem%3EFriends%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0aired%20in%202004%20after%20a%2010-year%20run%20that%20turned%20Perry%20and%20his%20cast%20mates%20into%20global%20celebrities.%20The%20show%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20TV%20shows%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFriends%E2%80%99%20was%20huge%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20jeopardize%20that.%20I%20loved%20the%20script.%20I%20loved%20my%20co-actors.%20I%20love%20the%20scripts%E2%80%A6%20but%20I%20was%20struggling%20with%20my%20addictions%20which%20only%20added%20to%20my%20sense%20of%20shame%2C%E2%80%9D%20Perry%20wrote%20in%20his%20memoir.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20secret%20and%20no%20one%20could%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmatthew-perry-friends-star-dies-at-54-reports%2Fa-67246497%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698559960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29114156%2Fb535ec42-07c4-484f-b4b7-99c6941f3d2c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Ffriends-star-matthew-perry-passes-away-at-54%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Perry%20received%20one%20Emmy%20nomination%20for%20his%20role%20in%20Friends%20and%20two%20more%20for%20appearances%20as%20an%20associate%20White%20House%20counsel%20on%20the%20The%20West%20Wing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Ffriends-star-matthew-perry-passes-away-at-54%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada's%20New%20Visa%20Rule%20To%20Protect%20Indian%20Students%20From%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada%20is%20implementing%20a%20new%20verification%20process%20to%20combat%20student%20visa%20fraud%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20incident%20that%20occurred%20in%20June%20this%20year%2C%20involving%20700%20Indian%20students.%20Canada%20has%20not%20imposed%20a%20limit%20on%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students.%20On%20October%2027%2C%20Immigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20announced%20a%20set%20of%20initiatives%20designed%20to%20enhance%20the%20International%20Student%20Program%20and%20provide%20increased%20safeguards%20for%20legitimate%20students%20against%20fraudulent%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20following%20measures%20have%20been%20introduced%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EStarting%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20post-secondary%20designated%20learning%20institutions%20(DLIs)%20will%20be%20required%20to%20verify%20the%20acceptance%20letters%20of%20all%20applicants%20with%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%2C%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC).%20This%20enhanced%20verification%20process%20aims%20to%20protect%20prospective%20students%20from%20fraudulent%20acceptance%20letters%20and%20prevent%20issues%20similar%20to%20those%20experienced%20by%20some%20students%20earlier%20this%20year%20due%20to%20fraud%20investigations.%20It%20will%20also%20ensure%20that%20study%20permits%20are%20only%20issued%20to%20applicants%20with%20genuine%20acceptance%20letters.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBy%20the%20fall%20semester%20of%202024%2C%20IRCC%20will%20implement%20a%20%26quot%3Brecognized%20institution%26quot%3B%20framework%20specifically%20aimed%20at%20benefiting%20post-secondary%20DLIs%20that%20excel%20in%20providing%20exceptional%20services%2C%20support%2C%20and%20outcomes%20for%20international%20students.%20These%20designated%20learning%20institutions%20(DLIs)%20will%20receive%20special%20treatment%2C%20including%20expedited%20processing%20of%20study%20permit%20applications%20for%20students%20intending%20to%20enroll%20in%20their%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20IRCC%20will%20conduct%20an%20evaluation%20of%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20Post-Graduation%20Work%20Permit%20Program.%20Reforms%20will%20be%20introduced%20to%20better%20align%20the%20program%20with%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20Canadian%20job%20market%2C%20as%20well%20as%20regional%20and%20Francophone%20immigration%20objectives.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20changes%20aim%20to%20protect%20genuine%20students%20from%20fraudulent%20activities%20and%20prioritise%20institutions%20that%20support%20international%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fpunjab-ministerurges-s-jaishankar-to-help-700-indian-students-facing-deportation-from-canada-4100554%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20Punjab%20Minister%20Urges%20S%20Jaishankar%20To%20Help%20Students%20Facing%20Deportation%20From%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Miller%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20enhancing%20the%20International%20Student%20Program%20to%20safeguard%20students%20and%20combat%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternational%20students%20are%20talented%2C%20bright%20and%20deserving%20of%20a%20positive%20experience%20as%20they%20pursue%20their%20studies%20in%20Canada.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20improve%20Canada's%20International%20Student%20Programme%20by%20protecting%20students%20and%20weeding%20out%20those%20who%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20them.%20Whether%20an%20international%20student%20stays%20and%20works%20after%20graduation%20or%20returns%20home%2C%20we%20want%20their%20time%20as%20a%20student%20in%20Canada%20to%20have%20been%20beneficial%20to%20their%20growth%20and%20aspirations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20an%20IRCC%20task%20force%20was%20created%20to%20address%20fraudulent%20admission%20letters%2C%20working%20with%20the%20Canada%20Border%20Services%20Agency%20(CBSA).%20Their%20goal%20was%20to%20prevent%20legitimate%20students%20from%20facing%20deportation.%20As%20of%20October%2012%2C%202023%2C%20out%20of%20103%20reviewed%20cases%2C%2063%20were%20confirmed%20as%20genuine%20students%2C%20while%2040%20were%20not.%20The%20task%20force%20is%20aware%20of%20more%20cases%20awaiting%20review%20pending%20decisions%20from%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Refugee%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2023%2C%202023%2C%20CBSA%20announced%20charges%20against%20Brijesh%20Mishra%20for%20immigration-related%20offenses%2C%20as%20he%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20defrauding%20students.%20IRCC%20will%20continue%20to%20collaborate%20with%20CBSA%20to%20identify%20and%20take%20action%20against%20individuals%20exploiting%20legitimate%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698559860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F6fvgia88_canada-visa-generic_625x300_03_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcanadas-new-visa-rule-to-protect-indian-students-from-fraud-4524542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada's%20New%20Student%20Visa%20Rule%3A%20Starting%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20post-secondary%20designated%20learning%20institutions%20(DLIs)%20will%20be%20required%20to%20verify%20the%20acceptance%20letters%20of%20all%20applicants%20with%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%2C%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcanadas-new-visa-rule-to-protect-indian-students-from-fraud-4524542%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcanadas-new-visa-rule-to-protect-indian-students-from-fraud-4524542%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcanadas-new-visa-rule-to-protect-indian-students-from-fraud-4524542%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Matthew's%20heart%20had%20stopped