cial%20statement%20released%20by%20India%20regarding%20the%20conversation%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20president%20provided%20a%20readout.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.presidency.eg%2Fen%2F%25D9%2582%25D8%25B3%25D9%2585-%25D8%25A7%25D9%2584%25D8%25A3%25D8%25AE%25D8%25A8%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B1%2F%25D8%25A3%25D8%25AE%25D8%25A8%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B1-%25D8%25B1%25D8%25A6%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B3%25D9%258A%25D8%25A9%2Far-28102023%2F%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20El-Sisi%20%E2%80%9Creceived%E2%80%9D%20the%20phone%20call%20from%20the%20Indian%20leader%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20leaders%20exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20latest%20developments%20in%20the%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20current%20escalation%2C%20given%20its%20formidable%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20civilians%20and%20the%20threat%20it%20poses%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20entire%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement%20issued%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20Modi%20had%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20and%20Jordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20talk%20also%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unannounced%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20after%2020%20days%20of%20retaliatory%20airstrikes%20which%20have%20reportedly%20left%20over%207%2C000%20dead.%20The%20latest%20escalation%20began%20after%20Hamas%20intruded%20into%20southern%20Israel%2C%20killing%20around%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20over%20200%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEl-Sisi%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20Egyptian%20president%20briefed%20about%20Cairo%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccoordinate%20regional%20and%20international%20efforts%20to%20push%20toward%20reaching%20a%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3EIndia%20on%20Saturday%20abstained%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20did%20not%20back%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20that%20called%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20%E2%80%9Ctruce%E2%80%9D%20to%20allow%20for%20unhindered%20supply%20of%20essential%20provisions%20to%20Gaza%20Strip.%20The%20resolution%20had%20been%20tabled%20by%20Jordan%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Arab%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Egyptian%20president%20warned%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgrievous%20humanitarian%20and%20security%20repercussions%20of%20a%20ground%20offensive%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20explicitly%20terming%20it%20as%20a%20ground%20invasion%2C%20Israel%20has%20announced%20the%20start%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20stage%20of%20the%20war%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Israeli%20military%20entering%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%2C%20which%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Gaza%20and%20Israel%2C%20has%20been%20the%20focus%20of%20international%20effort%20to%20get%20humanitarian%20supplies%20to%20civilians%20amidst%20the%20constant%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Egyptian%20leader%20highlighted%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccritical%20need%20for%20unified%20international%20action%20to%20find%20a%20prompt%20solution%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20level%2C%20that%20stipulates%20reinforcing%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20truce%20that%20protects%20the%20lives%20of%20civilians%20and%20allows%20the%20instantaneous%2C%20sustainable%20and%20unfettered%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20words%20echoed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2023%2Fga12548.doc.htm%5C%22%3Eprovisions%20of%20the%20UNGA%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20adopted%20with%20120%20votes%20in%20favour%2C%2014%20against%20and%2045%20abste