com%2Fsun-surface-photos-video-reveal-boiling-plasma-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20surface%20of%20the%20sun%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20says%20the%20super%20hot%20temperature%20ensures%20that%20the%20nonstick%20coating%20on%20its%20pans%20is%20more%20resistant%20than%20competitor%20pans%20made%20at%20lower%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20proposed%20class-action%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.classaction.org%2Fmedia%2Fbrown-v-sharkninja-operating-llc.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20against%20the%20company%2C%20New%20Jersey%20native%20Patricia%20Brown%20argues%20that%20SharkNinja's%20claims%20are%20physically%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20purchased%20two%2012-inch%2C%20nonstick%20frying%20pans%20made%20by%20SharkNinja%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20SharkNinja%20advertised%20the%20pans%20under%20the%20premise%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20%26quot%3Bstick%2C%20chip%2C%20or%20flake%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20had%20been%20manufactured%20at%20a%20scorching%20hot%20temperature%20of%2030%2C000%C2%B0F%2C%20unlike%20pans%20made%20at%20just%20900%C2%B0F%20that%20%26quot%3Brapidly%20lose%20nonstick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20says%20that%20claim%20is%20%26quot%3Blittle%20more%20than%20a%20glitzy%2C%20deceptive%20marketing%20technique%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20New%20Jersey%20District%20Court%20on%20October%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20says%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20SharkNinja's%20nearly%20%2460%20pans%20lose%20their%20nonstick%20coating%20more%20rapidly%20than%20competitor%20pans%20priced%20under%20%2410%20or%20%2420%20and%20that%20manufacturing%20pans%20at%20a%20temperature%20of%2030%2C000%C2%B0F%20%26quot%3Bdefies%20the%20laws%20of%20physics%20and%20thermodynamics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20company's%20product%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D469e421c5c16ef18bfc8a1