0need%20to%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing.%20As%20per%20the%20notice%2C%20importers%20of%20these%20items%20would%20need%20permission%20or%20license%20from%20the%20government%20for%20their%20inbound%20shipments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20on%20August%204%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20announced%20that%20implementation%20has%20been%20deferred%20till%20November%201%2C%20reportedly%20to%20allow%20the%20industry%20to%20adjust.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20restrict%20imports%20was%20to%20encourage%20Indian%20manufacturers%20since%20electronic%20imports%20accounted%20for%20%2419.7%20billion%20between%20April%20and%20June%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20several%20large%20companies%20directly%20impacted%20by%20the%20restrictions%2C%20the%20government%20had%20to%20make%20some%20relaxations.%20On%20October%2019%2C%20India%20unveiled%20a%20new%20liberal%20online%20authorisation%20system%20designed%20to%20automatically%20grant%20import%20authorisations%20once%20importers%20input%20the%20details%20regarding%20the%20value%2C%20volume%2C%20and%20source%20country%20of%20their%20intended%20imports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20authorisations%2C%20which%20come%20with%20no%20quantity%20or%20source%20restrictions%2C%20will%20remain%20valid%20until%20September%2030%2C%202024.%20Officials%20say%20the%20data%20collected%20during%20this%20monitoring%20period%20would%20inform%20future%20policy%20decisions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20representation%20to%20WTO%20noted%20that%20on%20September%2026%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20%E2%80%9Cannounced%20that%20on%20November%201%2C%202023%2C%20importers%20will%20only%20be%20required%20to%20register%20on%20an%20%E2%80%98import%20management%20system%E2%80%99%20in%20order%20to%20import%20regulated%20products%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20no%20change%20was%20made%20to%20the%20original%20notification%20(of%20August%203)%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20official%20representation%2C%20the%20United%20States%20requested%20that%20India%20provide%20details%20on%20the%20data%20to%20be%20gathered%20and%20its%20intended%20purpose.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20the%20information%20impact%20the%20process%20for%20granting%20licenses%3F%20Is%20India%20considering%20the%20use%20of%20quantitative%20restrictions%20based%20on%20the%20information%20supplied%3F%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%20also%20inquired%20whether%20India%20intended%20to%20broaden%20the%20scope%20of%20import%20licensing%20beyond%20the%20specified%20products%2C%20whether%20it%20had%20issued%20a%20public%20notification%20and%20allowed%20for%20a%20period%20of%20public%20comment%20before%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698496150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28173408%2Fpexels-olena-bohovyk-3550484.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fwto-us-questions-india-import-licenses-electronics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20also%20inquired%20whether%20India%20intended%20to%20broaden%20the%20scope%20of%20import%20licensing%20beyond%20the%20specified%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fwto-us-questions-india-import-licenses-electronics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Killers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Testament%20to%20One%20of%20the%20Greatest%20Living%20Filmmakers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28171205%2Fimage-1447.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20early%201920s%20in%20Fairfax%20(Oklahoma)%2C%20home%20to%20native%20Americans%20of%20the%20Osage%20nation%2C%20where%20suspicion%20and%20death%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiscovering%20huge%20reserves%20of%20oil%20on%20the%20land%20allotted%20to%20them%20by%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20the%20Osage%20tribe%20became%20some%20of%20the%20richest%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20early%20on%20in%20Martin%20Scorsese%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20they%E2%80%99re%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98sickly%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20them%20dying%20under%20mysterious%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20them%20know%20something%20is%20not%20quite%20right%20in%20Fairfax%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20to%20be%20certain.%20In%20a%20scene%2C%20an%20elder%20of%20the%20tribe%20bemoans%20how%20a%20decade%20ago%20when%20Osages%20were%20being%20hunted%2C%20he%20could%20at%20least%20see%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdapted%20from%20David%20Grann%E2%80%99s%20excellent%202014%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20Scorsese%20goes%20beyond%20Grann%E2%80%99s%20exhaustive%20reportage%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20exploring%20this%20horrifying%2C%20forgotten%20saga%20of%20American%20greed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpening%20the%20film%20with%20the%20late%20Robbie%20Robertson%E2%80%99s%20nifty%20guitar%20score%20playing%20in%20the%20background%2C%20Scorsese%20carefully%20sets%20the%20scene%20for%20his%20audience.%20Telling%20them%20about%20the%20sudden%20riches%20of%20the%20Osages%2C%20he%20introduces%20them%20to%20his%20protagonist%3A%20Ernest%20Burkhart%20(Leonardo%20DiCaprio).%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fascinating%2C%20counter-intuitive%20choice%2C%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20a%20great%20%E2%80%98American%20betrayal%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20side%20of%20the%20perpetrator%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20victims.%20Grann%E2%80%99s%20novel%20rarely%20delves%20beyond%20the%20most%20perfunctory%20characterisations%2C%20but%20Scorsese%20stamps%20his%20own%20authorship%20by%20imbuing%20life%20into%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20three%20primary%20characters%3A%20Ernest%20Burkhart%2C%20Mollie%20Kyle%20and%20Bill%20Hale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Burkhart%2C%20DiCaprio%20goes%20for%20what%20could%20only%20be%20described%20as%20a%20wildly%20anti-Gatsby%20look.%20His%20teeth%20are%20stained%2C%20the%20blue%20eyes%20seem%20to%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20a%20colourful%20youngster%20who%20has%20culminated%20into%20a%20diseased%20middle-age.%20He%20sports%20an%20awkward%20crew%20cut%20with%20messy%20hair%2C%20rightly%20for%20someone%20returning%20from%20the%20World%20War%2C%20even%20though%20he%20only%20worked%20in%20the%20pantry%2C%20serving%20those%20who%20were%20serving%20on%20the%20frontlines.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20humanity%20to%20him%2C%20where%20we%20see%20his%20slobbering%20greed%2C%20remorselessness%2C%20charm%20and%20sincerity%20all%20at%20once.%20Being%20coached%20by%20his%20uncle%20Bill%20Hale%20(Robert%20De%20Niro)%20to%20marry%20Mollie%20Kyle%20(Lily%20Gladstone)%2C%20who%20has%20a%20partial%20headright%20(claim%20to%20the%20lands%20producing%20oil)%20along%20with%20her%20mother%20Lizzie%2C%20and%20sisters%20Anna%2C%20Reta%20and%20Minnie.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrann%E2%80%99s%20book%20stresses%20upon%20the%20whole%20magnitude%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20so%20he%20approaches%20it%20through%20the%20police%20investigation%20of%20the%20murders%2C%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20FBI%20(Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation)%20led%20by%20J.%20Edgar%20Hoover%2C%20and%20the%20courtroom%20drama%20aided%20by%20the%20systemic%20rot.%20But%20here%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20screenplay%20by%20Eric%20Roth%20and%20Scorsese%20reveals%20itself.%20The%20film%20looks%20at%20the%20whole%20story%20through%20the%20marriage%20of%20Ernest%20and%20Mollie.%20Hale%20convinces%20his%20nephew%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20wealth%20to%20be%20had%2C%20and%20the%20Osages%20are%20merely%20obstacles%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20need%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hale%20tells%20other%20characters%2C%20more%20than%20once%20in%20the%20film.%20De%20Niro%20is%20masterfully%20unsentimental%20as%20he%20looks%20people%20in%20the%20eye%2C%20telling%20them%20how%20much%20he%20cares%20for%20them%2C%20and%20then%20pronounces%20their%20death%20warrants%20to%20his%20minions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20stunning%20attributes%20about%20Scorsese%E2%80%99s%20film%20here%20is%20how%20he%20makes%20the%20mass%20killings%20of%20the%20Osages%20feel%20like%20an%20order%20of%20business.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20chilling%20mundanity%20to%20the%20murders.%20In%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20lesser%20filmmaker%2C%20this%20deliberate%20genocide%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20milked%20for%20tears%20and%20screams.%20But%20in%20%3Cem%3EKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20death%20comes%20with%20a%20certain%20serenity%20and%20silence.%20The%20Osages%20have%20visions%20of%20an%20owl%20visiting%20them%20%E2%80%93%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98death%20is%20at%20your%20door.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20soul%20of%20the%20film%20is%20Ernest%20Burkhart%E2%80%99s%20imperfect%20evil.%20As%20much%20as%20he%20lusts%20after%20material%20wealth%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20genuinely%20in%20love%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20loyal%20to%20his%20uncle%2C%20unable%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20stack%20of%20corpses%20left%20behind%20in%20his%20pursuit%20fuelled%20by%20greed.%20Ernest%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20he%20is%20like%20his%20uncle%2C%20but%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20stomach%20for%20it.%20And%20that%20makes%20the%20betrayal%20that%20much%20more%20personal.%20How%20does%20one%20claim%20to%20love%20someone%2C%20and%20slowly%20poison%20them%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%3F%20Does%20their%20repentance%20count%20for%20anything%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELily%20Gladstone%20is%20impeccable%20as%20Mollie%2C%20a%20headstrong%20Osage%20woman%20who%20knows%20something%20is%20not%20quite%20right%2C%20but%20she%20just%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20believe.%20As%20Mollie%2C%20Gladstone%E2%80%99s%20performance%20is%20like%20that%20of%20a%20placid%20lake%20to%20DiCaprio%E2%80%99s%20Ernest%2C%20a%20tempestuous%20ocean.%20DiCaprio%E2%80%99s%20stunning%20performance%20reminded%20me%20of%20two%20earlier%20films%20%3Cem%3ERevolutionary%20Road%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2008)%20and%20%3Cem%3EShutter%20Island%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2010)%2C%20where%20he%20also%20played%20a%20husband%20drowning%20in%20his%20own%20guilt.%20I%20can%20think%20of%20at%20least%20two%20scenes%20where%20DiCaprio%20showcases%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20highest-rated%20actors%20of%20his%20generation.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sublime%20turn%20as%20someone%20grappling%20with%20opposite%20ends%20of%20his%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20206%20minutes%2C%20%3Cem%3EKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20long%20film%2C%20but%20rarely%20drags.%20Scorsese%20knows%20exactly%20when%20to%20hit%20the%20brakes%20on%20his%20brisk%20narrative%2C%20allowing%20the%20viewers%20to%20soak%20in%20the%20tension.%20There%E2%80%99s%20an%20unsettling%20exchange%20between%20Ernest%20and%20Tom%20White%20(Jesse%20Plemons)%20%E2%80%93%20sent%20by%20the%20FBI%20to%20investigate%20the%20Osage%20murders%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20all%20the%20hints%20of%20the%20eventual%20unravelling.%20Seeing%20White%20at%20his%20door%2C%20Ernest%20knows%20immediately%20that%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20is%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20%3Cem%3EKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20living%20filmmakers%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20Martin%20Scorsese.%20The%2080-year-old%20director%20takes%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dense%20books%2C%20and%20manages%20to%20locate%20the%20people%20at%20its%20core.%20He%20humanises%20these%20evil%20masterminds%20without%20necessarily%20showing%20mercy%20for%20their%20devious%20ways.%20This%20is%20a%20masterful%20adaptation%20that%20distils%20the%20larger%20injustice%20to%20a%20community%2C%20by%20boiling%20it%20down%20to%20a%20marriage%20between%20an%20Osage%20woman%20and%20her%20greedy%2C%20conflicted%20white%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20way%20he%20conveys%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20which%20most%20movies%20might%E2%80%99ve%20done%20using%20title%20cards%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20Scorsese%20employs%20a%20live%20radio%20show%20with%20foley%20artists%2C%20replete%20with%20a%20special%20appearance.%20However%2C%20the%20special%20appearance%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20out%20of%20humility%20than%20a%20gimmick.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20veteran%20grappling%20with%20his%20choice%20of%20medium%2C%20using%20it%20to%20look%20within%20and%20the%20society%20around%20him.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20sincerely%20feeling%20the%20injustice%20in%20the%20story%20you%E2%80%99re%20telling%2C%20and%20conveying%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20people%20leave%20the%20theatre%20in%20stunned%20silence.%20Now%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698494411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28171205%2Fimage-1447.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fkillers-of-the-flower-moon-is-a-testament-to-one-of-the-greatest-living-filmmakers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Killers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon'%20is%20a%20long%20film%2C%20but%20rarely%20drags.%20Martin%20Scorsese%20knows%20exactly%20when%20to%20hit%20the%20brakes%20on%20his%20brisk%20narrative%2C%20allowing%20the%20viewers%20to%20soak%20in%20the%20tension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fkillers-of-the-flower-moon-is-a-testament-to-one-of-the-greatest-living-filmmakers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Appeal%20To%20the%20UN%20Chief%3A%20Understand%20Nepal%20Beyond%20the%20Prevalent%20Caricatures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28164437%2F51321104713_f5b39c48a1_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20has%20been%20vital%20to%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20modern%20era%2C%20marking%20the%20vulnerable%20country%E2%80%99s%20international%20standing%20through%20membership%20in%20the%20organisation%20in%20December%201955%2C%20providing%20development%20advisory%20and%20assistance%20over%20the%20decades%20outside%20the%20prism%20of%20geopolitical%20considerations.%20Nepal%2C%20too%2C%20has%20assisted%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20most%20importantly%20as%20the%20country%20now%20providing%20the%20second%20largest%20contingent%20to%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20peacekeeping%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20time%2C%20though%2C%20this%20relationship%20took%20a%20beating.%20There%20were%20several%20factors%2C%20but%20mainly%20it%20was%20the%20insensitivities%20of%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Mission%20to%20Nepal%20(UNMIN)%2C%20which%20helped%20ignite%20a%20reactive%20political%20class%20and%20bureaucracy%20in%20Kathmandu.%20The%20passage%20of%20time%20has%20provided%20some%20healing%2C%20but%20proactive%20measures%20are%20needed%20to%20rebuild%20empathy%2C%20and%20a%20visit%20of%20the%20secretary-general%20provides%20an%20opportunity%20even%20though%20there%20has%20been%20little%20time%20for%20any%20of%20the%20stakeholders%20to%20plan%2C%20least%20of%20all%20Nepali%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20for%20Nepal%20that%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20world%20body%20is%20normalised%20at%20an%20accelerated%20pace%2C%20because%20Nepal%20needs%20a%20friendly%20arm%20amidst%20the%20escalating%20great-power%20rivalries%20of%20Asia%20and%20globally%2C%20and%20with%20it%20the%20clamour%20for%20Kathmandu%20to%20take%20sides.%20The%20planned%20visit%20of%20UN%20secretary-general%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20on%20October%2029%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20revitalise%20the%20UN-Nepal%20connection%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20curiosity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20first-time%20plenipotentiary%20to%20Kathmandu%20must%20seek%20first-hand%20knowledge%20on%20Nepal%20and%20its%20recent%20experiences%2C%20particularly%20the%20conflict%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20put%20behind%2C%20for%20neither%20journalistic%20nor%20academic%20writings%20are%20adequate%20for%20a%20country%20that%20functions%20outside%20the%20colonial%20language%20discourse.%20Further%2C%20as%20is%20well%20known%2C%20the%20institutional%20memory%20of%20the%20international%20agencies%20and%20diplomatic%20corps%20is%20notoriously%20wanting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERight%20off%2C%20while%20it%20is%20a%20privilege%20for%20a%20country%20that%20has%20been%20shunned%20for%20long%20by%20world%20leaders%20to%20receive%20a%20high%20personage%2C%20it%20is%20a%20curiosity%20that%20the%20UN%20secretary-general%20has%20chosen%20to%20visit%20Nepal%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20ruled%20by%20a%20prime%20minister%20whose%20party%20has%2032%20seats%20in%20a%20parliament%20of%20275%20(11.1%25)%20and%20whose%20hold%20on%20power%20is%20precarious.%20Maoist%20chairman%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20(%3Cem%3Enom%20de%20guerre%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%98Prachanda%E2%80%99)%20does%20not%20represent%20the%20choice%20for%20head%20of%20government%20in%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20ballot%20of%20November%202022.%20He%20is%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20seat%20because%20of%20the%20dog-eat-dog%20nature%20of%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20forever%20full-time%20politicians%2C%20competing%20embassies%20with%20geopolitical%20urgencies%2C%20and%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20mix%20of%20direct-proportional%20electoral%20system.%20The%20public%20does%20accept%20the%20de%20jure%20reality%20and%20is%20simply%20waiting%20for%20the%20wheel%20to%20turn%20%E2%80%93%20one%20may%20be%20properly%20legal%20but%20not%20carry%20legitimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20there%20is%20a%20reading%20of%20the%20collective%20mind%2C%20with%20which%20this%20writer%20agrees%2C%20that%20everyone%20is%20simply%20waiting%20for%20the%20house%20of%20cards%20to%20collapse.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Dahal%20regime%20has%20entered%20deeper%20into%20the%20swamp%20of%20corruption%20and%20mal-governance%20than%20previous%20ones%2C%20including%20derailing%20investigations%20into%20several%20cases%20of%20loot%20relating%20to%20gold%20smuggling%2C%20fake%20refugees%20and%20government%20land%20made%20private%3B%20it%20cannot%20hold%20its%20head%20high%20among%20international%20peers%3B%20it%20is%20happy%20with%20the%20weakening%20of%20state%20institutions%20and%20revels%20in%20defying%20Supreme%20Court%20injunctions%3B%20it%20lacks%20economic%20vision%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%20brimming%20in%20natural%20and%20human%20resources%3B%20it%20lacks%20the%20credibility%20to%20handle%20proximate%20challenges%20to%20social%20harmony%3B%20and%2C%20it%20does%20not%20seem%20energised%20to%20battle%20those%20working%20to%20engineer%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%202015%20Constitution.%20No%20other%20head%20of%20government%20of%20the%2073%20years%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Rana%20autocracy%20is%20this%20much%20driven%20by%20personal%20rather%20than%20national%20ambition%2C%20and%20publicly%20willing%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98comfortable%E2%80%99%20with%20whichever%20neighbouring%20government%20will%20back%20his%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lumbini%20garden%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20finest%20contributions%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20organisation%20in%20Nepal%20was%20triggering%20the%20preservation%20and%20development%20of%20Lumbini%20and%20its%20surrounding%20area.%20The%20management%20of%20the%20nativity%20site%20of%20the%20Sakyamuni%2C%20however%2C%20presents%20an%20example%20of%20the%20inadequacies%20of%20Nepali%20governance%2C%20and%20where%20the%20UN%20may%20want%20to%20re-engage%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20secretaries-general%20who%20have%20arrived%20in%20Kathmandu%20have%20made%20the%20trip%20to%20Lumbini%2C%20and%20one%20expects%20Guterres%20will%2C%20too.%20The%20third%20incumbent%2C%20U-Thant%2C%20arrived%20here%20in%201967%2C%20wept%20with%20emotion%2C%20and%20vouched%20to%20provide%20support%20to%20develop%20the%20place.%20King%20Mahendra%20enthusiastically%20took%20up%20the%20idea%2C%20and%20the%20plans%20presented%20by%20architect%20Kenzo%20Tange%20have%20saved%20the%20immediate%20area%20from%20being%20commercialised%20beyond%20repair%2C%20managed%20as%20it%20has%20been%20by%20political%20appointees%20who%20care%20little%20about%20preserving%20the%20spiritual%20sanctity%20of%20a%20site%20that%20is%20heritage%20of%20all%20humankind.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20first%20visit%20to%20Lumbini%20by%20a%20UN%20head%20was%20in%201959%2C%20when%20the%20second%20Secretary-General%20Dag%20Hammarskjold%20touched%20down%20and%20also%20wrote%20a%20haiku%2C%20published%20in%20a%20posthumous%20collection%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELike%20glittering%20sunbeams%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20flute%20notes%20reach%20the%20gods%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20birth%20grotto.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sanctity%20of%20Lumbini%20was%20clearly%20felt%20by%20Hammerskjold%2C%20the%20Nepali%20custodians%20have%20been%20lax%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20challenge%20today%20is%20to%20save%20Lumbini%20from%20over-marketing%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20spirituality%2C%20ratchet%20down%20competing%20Buddhist%20nationalisms%20and%20inter-sect%20competition%2C%20and%20find%20a%20way%20to%20tackle%20the%20projected%20massive%20increase%20in%20footfall%20of%20pilgrims%20and%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELumbini%20is%20the%20only%20heritage%20site%20that%20has%20a%20body%20dedicated%20to%20the%20UN%20Headquarters%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20International%20Committee%20for%20the%20Development%20of%20Lumbini%20was%20set%20in%20motion%20by%20U-Thant%20with%20Buddhist%20countries%20forming%20its%20membership.%20The%20Committee%20has%20been%20moribund%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20and%20the%20Nepal%20government%20is%20required%20to%20work%20with%20the%20UN%20to%20consider%20re-activating%20it%20to%20address%20all%20matters%20from%20preservation%20and%20archaeology%2C%20to%20landscaping%2C%20aesthetics%20and%20fund-raising.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecretary-general%20Guterres%20will%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20that%20PM%20Dahal%20has%20just%20appointed%20a%20monk%20of%20dubious%20antecedents%20as%20head%20of%20the%20Lumbini%20Development%20Trust%20(LDT)%20which%20oversees%20both%20Lumbini%20and%20Kapilvastu%2C%20the%20hometown%20of%20Sakyamuni.%20A%20newspaper%20article%20described%20the%20LDT%20chief%E2%80%99s%20past%20in%20these%20words%2C%20as%20he%20took%20charge%20in%20August%20this%20year%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20earlier%20been%20charged%20with%20several%20crimes%2C%20including%20foreign%20employment%20fraud%2C%20possession%20of%20illegal%20firearms%2C%20accumulating%20property%20disproportionate%20to%20his%20known%20source%20of%20income%2C%20and%20possession%20of%20dual%20citizenship%20and%20passport.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurder%20commonplace%2C%20or%20malicious%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20divulging%20no%20state%20secret%20in%20saying%20that%20Nepal%20has%20a%20prime%20minister%20whose%20party%2C%20having%20failed%20miserably%20in%20the%20first%20democratic%20elections%20of%201991%2C%20organised%20and%20went%20underground%20to%20wage%20insurrection%20against%20parliamentary%20democracy%20in%201996.%20Having%20caused%20enough%20mayhem%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20insurgency%2C%20the%20rebel%20leaders%20struck%20a%20deal%20to%20land%20right%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20The%20so-called%20%E2%80%98people%E2%80%99s%20war%E2%80%99%20was%20not%20waged%20against%20an%20autocratic%20royal%20regime%2C%20as%20believed%20by%20many%20foreign%20diplomats%20and%20even%20scholars.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20credit%20for%20the%20pluralism%20and%20democracy%20we%20enjoy%20today%20is%20thanks%20to%20the%201990%20constitution%2C%20whose%20democratic%20foundations%20held%20firm%20even%20as%20the%202015%20constitution%20was%20readied.%20The%20Maoist%20leaders%E2%80%99%20own%20favoured%20document%2C%20which%20they%20tried%20to%20push%20through%2C%20resembled%20the%20constitution%20of%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20flaw%20in%20the%20man%20who%20is%20the%20present%20head%20of%20government%20has%20been%20the%20enthusiastic%20promotion%20of%20extrajudicial%20killing%20of%20citizens%2C%20added%20to%20that%20his%20refusal%20till%20this%20day%20to%20express%20remorse%20or%20set%20the%20course%20for%20accountability%20for%20excesses%20committed%2C%20an%20exercise%20to%20rope%20in%20both%20insurgent%20and%20state-side%20perpetrators.%20After%20he%20came%20above%20ground%2C%20Dahal%20said%20in%20a%20live%20BBC%20Nepali%20Service%20interview%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cpersonally%20issued%20a%20circular%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20insurgency%20instructing%20cadres%20to%20annihilate%20victims%20without%20first%20torturing%20them%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20talk%20of%20admission%20of%20command%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20disdain%20for%20targeted%20victims%20is%20palpable%20in%20the%20Transitional%20Justice%20Bill%20that%20the%20government%20has%20submitted%20to%20parliament%2C%20drafted%20at%20PM%20Dahal%E2%80%99s%20behest%20by%20a%20turncoat%20human%20rights%20lawyer%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20distinguish%20between%20%E2%80%98commonplace%20murder%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98malicious%20murder%E2%80%99.%20Dahal%E2%80%99s%20flippancy%20regarding%20the%20lives%20of%20citizens%20was%20evident%20again%20in%20January%202020%2C%20when%20he%20told%20a%20gathering%20that%20he%20would%20take%20responsibility%20for%205%2C000%20dead%20during%20the%20insurgency%20if%20others%20took%20responsibility%20for%20the%20remaining%2012%2C000.%20There%20is%20a%20case%20being%20heard%20on%20this%20count%20against%20him%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20Maoist%20leaders%20used%20child%20soldiers%20with%20abandon%2C%20but%20neither%20the%20international%20community%20nor%20the%20national%20polity%20seemed%20greatly%20bothered%2C%20then%20or%20now.%20The%20United%20Nations%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20should%20be%2C%20for%20it%20was%20UNMIN%20which%20certified%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20Maoist%20child%20soldiers%2C%20yet%20failed%20to%20find%20them%20a%20safe%20landing%20as%20it%20packed%20its%20bags%20and%20departed.%20It%20has%20been%20left%20to%20the%20former%20child%20soldiers%20to%20challenge%20the%20state%20establishment%20all%20alone%2C%20wanting%20to%20be%20counted%2C%20compensated%20and%20healed.%20PM%20Dahal%E2%80%99s%20personal%20effort%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%98child%20combatants%E2%80%99%20out%20of%20the%20TJ%20Bill%20he%20submitted%20that%20is%20being%20worked%20on%20by%20a%20committee%20in%20parliament.%20His%20pressures%20on%20the%20committee%20members%20are%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07141514%2FPrachanda-Dahal.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07141514%2FPrachanda-Dahal.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07141514%2FPrachanda-Dahal-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07141514%2FPrachanda-Dahal-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07141514%2FPrachanda-Dahal-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662119%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20of%20Nepal%20Pushpa%20Kumar%20%E2%80%9CPrachanda%E2%80%9D%20Dahal.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40cmdahal%2C%20July%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOHCHR%20and%20UNMIN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20phalanx%20of%20UN%20specialised%20agencies%20and%20organisations%20have%20been%20active%20in%20Nepal%20for%20decades%2C%20from%20UNDP%20to%20FAO%20to%20WHO%20to%20UN%20Women%2C%20playing%20catalytic%20roles%20in%20so%20many%20arenas%20in%20a%20country%20that%20arrived%20late%20into%20open%20society%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98era%20of%20development%E2%80%99.%20Sadly%2C%20amidst%20all%20this%2C%20the%20society%20was%20diverted%20for%20a%20full%20decade%20by%20the%20internal%20conflict%2C%20with%20another%20decade%20devoted%20to%20the%20peace%20process%20and%20constitution-writing%20with%20their%20attendant%20political%20instability.%20That%20is%20when%20the%20two%20offices%20took%20centre%20stage%2C%20OHCHR%20and%20UNMIN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Office%20of%20the%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(OHCHR)%20played%20an%20effective%20role%20during%20the%20conflict%20years.%20When%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20transitional%20justice%20project%20is%20finally%20rescued%20from%20saboteur%C2%A0politicians%20bent%20on%20making%20it%20a%20faux%20process%2C%20OHCHR%E2%80%99s%20long-forgotten%20%E2%80%98Nepal%20Conflict%20Report%E2%80%99%20(NCR)%20must%20be%20the%20main%20reference%20document%2C%20archiving%20as%20it%20does%2030%2C000%20papers%20on%20violation%20of%20international%20human%20rights%20law%20and%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20between%20February%201996%20and%20November%202006.%20The%20concluding%20%E2%80%98core%20messages%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20NCR%20to%20those%20meant%20to%20adopt%20and%20administer%20the%20Nepali%20transitional%20justice%20process%20are%2C%20in%20its%20own%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnder%20international%20law%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20has%20a%20fundamental%20obligation%20to%20investigate%20and%20prosecute%20serious%20violations%20of%20international%20human%20rights%20law%20and%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20that%20were%20committed%20during%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhere%20there%20is%20a%20reasonable%20basis%20for%20suspicion%20that%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20international%20law%20occurred%2C%20these%20cases%20merit%20prompt%20and%20independent%20investigation%20by%20a%20full%20judicial%20process.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20transitional%20justice%20mechanisms%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20transitional%20justice%20process%20but%20should%20complement%20criminal%20processes%20and%20not%20be%20an%20alternative%20to%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20prescriptions%20are%20being%20ignored%20blatantly%20by%20the%20national%20political%20parties%20old%20and%20new%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20the%20protests%20of%20conflict%20victims%20and%20rights%20defenders%20that%20have%20kept%20the%20politicians%20from%20buckling%20completely%20to%20Dahal%E2%80%99s%20desires%20and%20demands.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Western%20government%20and%20West-based%20INGOs%20that%20enthusiastically%20pushed%20Transitional%20Justice%20into%20the%20Nepali%20slipstream%20themselves%20have%20gone%20cold%2C%20a%20result%20of%20%E2%80%98TJ%20fatigue%E2%80%99%20and%20newborn%20geopolitical%20calculations%2C%20it%20would%20seem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20person%20who%20headed%20OHCHR%20was%20assigned%20to%20lead%20UNMIN%20as%20the%20Secretary-General%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Representative.%20This%20writer%20was%20among%20those%20who%20lobbied%20for%20his%20assignment%20to%20Nepal%2C%20knowing%20his%20earlier%20record.%20Incongruously%2C%20the%20gentleman%E2%80%99s%20tilt%20and%20tonality%20changed%20in%20the%20new%20position.%20Once%20a%20tussle%20for%20authority%20with%20the%20UNDP%20Resident%20Representative%20was%20resolved%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Special%20Representative%2C%20there%20was%20a%20shift%20in%20UNMIN%E2%80%99s%20focus%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20privilege%20the%20Maoist%20party%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20democratic%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20very%20forces%20which%20had%20made%20way%20for%20the%20rebels%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20the%20scorched%20earth%20policy%20that%20would%20have%20been%20implemented%20by%20the%20Army%2C%20which%20in%202005%20was%20under%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20direct%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maoist%20supremo%20and%20his%20party%20thus%20received%20an%20unexpected%20boost%20and%20bonus%20from%20UNMIN%20as%20they%20entered%20open%20politics%2C%20and%2C%20critically%2C%20UNMIN%20also%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20how%20the%20Western%20officialdom%20and%20academia%20viewed%20the%20Nepali%20polity.%20That%20view%20was%20a%20caricature%20of%20Nepali%20society%20as%20static%20and%20%E2%80%98Brahminical%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20little%20recognition%20of%20the%20complexities%20of%20Nepali%20history%20and%20inter-community%20relations%2C%20or%20the%20attempts%20to%20usher%20transformation%20through%20representative%20democracy%20after%201990.%20The%20Maoist%20commandants%20were%20regarded%20as%20true%20leaders%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20out%20to%20deconstruct%20a%20feudal%20state%20rather%20than%20simply%20wanting%20to%20supplant%20the%20incumbents.%20The%20trajectory%20of%20the%20Maoist%20leadership%20of%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20perception%20was%20faulty%2C%20but%20UNMIN%20is%20long%20disbanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20was%20ideological%20blinders%20at%20the%20top%20of%20UNMIN%2C%20an%20eye%20on%20a%20career%20ladder%20within%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20or%20simply%20activism%20gone%20wrong%2C%20the%20damage%20was%20done.%20Till%20today%2C%20much%20of%20how%20the%20Western%20world%20views%20the%20Nepali%20state%20establishment%20%E2%80%93%20and%20also%20why%20many%20ambassadors%20defer%20to%20Dahal%20as%20many%20do%2C%20beyond%20his%20position%20as%20prime%20minister%E2%80%93%20is%20defined%20by%20the%20bearing%20set%20by%20UNMIN%20and%20its%20first%20Special%20Representative.%20Without%20knowing%20what%20the%20Maoists%20did%20to%20rural%20Nepal%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20there%20have%20been%20individual%20Western%20ambassadors%20that%20one%20can%20name%20who%20have%20been%20simply%20enamoured%20of%20Dahal%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98revolutionary%E2%80%99%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20UNMIN%20was%20biased%2C%20neither%20was%20it%20diligent.%20One%20episode%20will%20suffice%20to%20prove%20the%20point%3A%20In%20May%202009%2C%20a%20video%20was%20leaked%20where%20Dahal%20is%20mirthfully%20sharing%20with%20his%20cadre%20how%20the%20Maoist%20had%20outright%20bamboozled%20UNMIN%20as%20it%20was%20carrying%20out%20verification%20of%20combatants.%20Barely%20able%20to%20hold%20back%20laughter%2C%20Dahal%20said%20while%20the%20Maoists%20had%20no%20more%20than%207-8000%20fighters%2C%20they%20had%20claimed%2035%2C000%2C%20and%20got%20UNMIN%20to%20agree%20to%2020%2C000.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20UNMIN%2C%20with%20its%20well-paid%20experts%20on%20all%20matters%20from%20peace-making%20to%20mass%20psychology%2C%20advised%20the%20Nepali%20authorities%20to%20go%20into%20the%202008%20elections%20with%20the%20inflated%20numbers%20of%20(armed)%20Maoists%20in%20the%20camps%20and%20threatening%20%E2%80%98to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20jungle%E2%80%99.%20That%20is%20when%20the%20Maoists%20got%20their%20most%20votes%20ever%2C%20by%20blackmailing%20the%20public%20and%20getting%20a%20momentum%20that%20has%20lasted%20them%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeither%20accounting%20nor%20accountability%20was%20sought%20of%20UNMIN%2C%20and%20it%20is%20indeed%20time%20to%20let%20bygones%20be%20bygones.%20But%20it%20would%20be%20a%20useful%20exercise%20for%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20peace-making%20and%20peace-building%20efforts%20if%20the%20secretary-general%20were%20to%20order%20a%20study%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20reports%20of%20UNMIN%20to%20verify%20the%20alleged%20partiality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20UN%20Alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20better%20the%20United%20Nations%20understands%20the%20Nepali%20reality%20and%20comes%20to%20its%20independent%20conclusions%20regarding%20the%20range%20of%20issues%20from%20transitional%20justice%20to%20human%20development%20and%20climate%20crisis%2C%20the%20easier%20it%20will%20be%20for%20the%20larger%20international%20community%20to%20come%20to%20a%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20experience%2C%20and%20how%20to%20partner%20with%20it%20for%20global%20good.%20For%20its%20part%2C%20Nepal%20is%20presently%20buffeted%20by%20multi-sided%20polarisations%20involving%20China%2C%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20West%20generally.%20It%20seems%20more%20impacted%20than%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20China-India%20periphery%2C%20perhaps%20due%20to%20its%20geographical%20positioning%20and%20landlocked%20nature.%20Within%20a%20suddenly%20fearsome%20international%20environment%20and%20shrill%20calls%20for%20joining%20this%2C%20that%2C%20or%20the%20other%20side%20%E2%80%93%20if%20there%20is%20a%20protective%20%E2%80%98alliance%E2%80%99%20Nepal%20needs%20to%20join%20it%20is%20one%20with%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecretary-general%20Guterres%20and%20his%20team%20will%20surely%20use%20the%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20observe%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20successes%20and%20assess%20its%20challenges.%20They%20will%20want%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Nepal%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%98small%E2%80%99%20country.%20It%20is%20regarded%20as%20such%20mainly%20because%20Nepal%20has%20land%20borders%20with%20two%20humongous%20neighbours%20and%20the%20size%20of%20its%20two%20other%20proximate%20neighbours%2C%20but%20Nepal%20is%20the%2048th%20largest%20country%20by%20population%20among%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20membership%20of%20193%20nation-states.%20While%20Nepal%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20assigned%20the%20%E2%80%98basket%20case%E2%80%99%20classificationthat%20earlier%20used%20to%20be%20the%20lot%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20are%20significant%20triumphs%20that%20are%20not%20propagated.%20Mark%20the%20fact%20that%20Nepal%20is%20the%20one%20large%20country%20of%20South%20Asia%20without%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20law%20and%20practice%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20only%20country%20where%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98transitional%20justice%E2%80%99%20is%20even%20uttered%3B%20each%20and%20every%20country%20has%20a%20history%20of%20long-term%20abuse%20of%20some%20part%20of%20the%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20Nepal%2C%20the%20international%20community%20could%20learn%3A%20how%20to%20adopt%20a%20constitution%20by%20elected%20constituent%20assembly%20unlike%20most%20experiences%20of%20appointed%20commissions%3B%20how%20to%20keep%20head%20above%20water%20amidst%20roiling%20and%20unrelenting%20international%20intervention%20over%20decades%3B%20how%20to%20prevent%20minority%20bashing%20and%20spread%20of%20inter-community%20conflagration%20within%20a%20Subcontinent%20that%20is%20becoming%20dangerously%20polarised%20by%20faith%3B%20%C2%A0and%2C%20how%20to%20keep%20borders%20open%20even%20as%20the%20trend%20elsewhere%20is%20to%20put%20up%20barbed%20wire%20and%20barricades.%20Nepal%20provides%20the%20neutral%20ground%20where%20all%20Southasians%20except%20Afghans%20are%20welcome%20with%20visa-on-arrival.%20Indians%20need%20merely%20ID%20cards%2C%20while%20Nepal%20as%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20SAARC%20organisation%20must%20consider%20removing%20the%20prior%20visa%20requirements%20for%20Afghanistan%20passport-holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20with%20all%20its%20flaws%20which%20include%20entrenched%20Kathmandu-centricism%20and%20historical%20marginalisation%20of%20mountain%2C%20hill%20and%20plain%20communities%2C%20Nepal%20is%20today%20(and%20thus%20far)%20the%20most%20open%20and%20democratic%20country%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20one%20that%20is%20willing%20to%20experiment%20with%20innovations%20that%20are%20suggested.%20Nepal%20needs%20to%20preserve%20its%20pluralism%20and%20democracy%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20its%20own%20population%20most%20importantly%2C%20but%20also%20to%20hold%20a%20lamp%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20subcontinent.%20It%20is%20therefore%20vital%20for%20UN%20officials%20to%20be%20alert%20to%20efforts%20underway%20to%20engineer%20constitutional%20collapse%20and%20a%20dismantling%20of%20democracy%2C%20if%20possible%20even%20a%20weakening%20of%20sovereign%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20decade%C2%A0of%20violent%20conflict%20and%20political%20turmoil%2C%20Nepal%20managed%20to%20reduce%20infant%20and%20maternal%20mortality%2C%20making%20a%20success%20of%20community%20forestry%2C%20and%20being%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20Subcontinent%20where%20radio%20broadcasting%20remains%20open%20for%20true%20public%20broadcasting.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20about%20to%20emerge%20from%20an%C2%A0under-developed%20country%20to%20developing%20country%20status%20says%20something%20about%20successfully%20fighting%20the%20odds.%20On%20human%20development%20and%20hunger%20indices%2C%20Nepal%20is%20doing%20better%20than%20next-door%20Indian%20states%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20so%20there%20is%20little%20cause%20for%20the%20national%20embarrassment%20that%20is%20felt%20by%20so%20many.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Nepal%20is%20the%20sixth%20to%20seventh%20largest%20remittance-sending%20country%20to%20India%2C%20that%20too%20providing%20survival%20sustenance%20to%20the%20poorest%20parts%20in%20an%20arc%20from%20Eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28164739%2Fpexels-sanam-magar-14633567.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28164739%2Fpexels-sanam-magar-14633567.jpg%20911w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28164739%2Fpexels-sanam-magar-14633567-300x265.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Nepali%20flag.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%3Cbr%3Esanam%20magar%2FPexels%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransitional%20justice%2C%20climate%20crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20that%20Nepal%20can%20finally%20end%20the%20peace%20process%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20to%20suffer%20another%20conflict%20like%20in%201996-2006%2C%20Secretary-general%20Guterres%E2%80%99%20United%20Nations%20should%20stand%20like%20a%20bastion%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20just%20end%20to%20the%20Transitional%20Justice%20process%2C%20particularly%20because%20those%20who%20introduced%20the%20concept%20themselves%20are%20no%20longer%20enthused.%20The%20Maoists%2C%20as%20well%20as%20lazy%20politicians%20and%20some%20commentators%20like%20to%20say%20flippantly%20that%20the%20process%20has%20to%20end%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20it%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20too%20long%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20if%20one%20must%20do%20a%20hasty%2C%20shoddy%20process%20just%20to%20please%20the%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ask%20the%20victims%20at%20large%20or%20their%20representatives%2C%20they%20are%20in%20a%20tearing%20rush%20to%20ensure%20reparation%2C%20but%20they%20do%20not%20want%20compromise%20on%20accountability%20for%20atrocities%20committed%20as%20we%20go%20in%20for%20truth%20and%20reconciliation.%20The%20victims%20do%20understand%20that%20if%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20TJ%20process%20that%20tackles%20emblematic%20cases%20of%20human%20rights%20excess%20under%20principles%20laid%20down%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20judgements%20and%20international%20law%20and%20practice%2C%20our%20society%20is%20doomed%20to%20a%20repetition%20of%20violent%20conflicts%20in%20the%20future.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20the%20issue%20of%20child%20soldiers%20is%20kept%20out%20of%20TJ%E2%80%99s%20purview%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20recruitment%C2%A0of%20underage%20citizens%20by%20extremists%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20travesty%20that%20is%20the%20Transitional%20Justice%20bill%20placed%20by%20the%20Government%20before%20Parliament%20was%20fortunately%20noticed%20by%20four%20United%20Nations%20Special%20Rapporteurs%2C%20who%20wrote%20to%20the%20Nepal%20Government%20on%209%20June%202023%20severely%20critiquing%20the%20document%20and%20warning%20that%20Nepal%20was%20set%20to%20defy%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%20To%20specific%20queries%20sent%20by%20the%20Special%20Rapporteurs%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20provided%20pro%20forma%20and%20inadequate%20answers%2C%20also%20hiding%20behind%20that%20fig%20leaf%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20now%20a%20%E2%80%98property%20of%20Parliament%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20take%20a%20few%20more%20years%2C%20but%20let%20us%20not%20rush%20the%20transitional%20justice%20process%20to%20please%20some%20Maoist%20leaders%20and%20select%20diplomats%20who%20may%20also%20see%20it%20as%20career%20enhancing.%20Nepali%20jurisprudence%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20already%20exists%20to%20push%20the%20%E2%80%98transitional%20justice%E2%80%99%20process%20to%20its%20ethical%20conclusion%2C%20and%20no%20one%20should%20think%20of%20going%20outside%20those%20strictures.%20A%20principled%20rather%20than%20a%20fraudulently%20practical%20end%20to%20the%20TJ%20process%20would%20be%20a%20great%20gift%20to%20the%20long%20suffering%20victimsof%20conflict.%20Properly%20watchdogging%20the%20process%20for%20false%20culminations%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20feather%20on%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20cap%20having%20safeguarded%20an%20important%20and%20exemplary%20process.%20Let%20future%20study%20tours%20from%20post-conflict%20societies%20visit%20Nepal%20as%20much%20as%20they%20do%20Colombia%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Dahal%20government%20single-mindedlytrying%20to%20foist%20an%20improper%20ending%20to%20the%20TJ%20process%2C%20and%20its%20other%20main%20focus%20being%20simply%20to%20survive%20in%20power%2C%20it%20has%20no%20desire%20or%20energy%20to%20have%20Nepal%20lead%20in%20any%20arena%20of%20international%20concern.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20climate%20crisis%20is%20one%20such%20area.%20The%20government%20does%20little%20beyond%20vacuously%20mouthglobal%20warming%20cliches%2C%20even%20as%20it%20cancelled%20a%20planned%20global%20climate%20summit%20titled%20%E2%80%98Sagarmatha%20Conclave%E2%80%99%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActionable%20Matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20globe%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98third%20pole%E2%80%99%20(the%20Himalaya)%2C%20Nepal%20serves%20as%20a%20veritable%20barometer%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20populated%20terrain%20going%20from%20tropical%20to%20alpine%20within%20a%20span%20of%20less%20than%20a%20hundred%20miles.%20Because%20glacial%20retreat%2C%20reduction%20in%20groundwater%20and%20river%20flows%2C%20melting%20of%20permafrost%20and%20extreme%20weather%20events%20impact%20not%20only%20the%20Himalaya%20but%20the%20entire%20downstream%20biosphere%2C%20it%20is%20from%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20populated%20mountains%20that%20the%20alarm%20will%20sound%20most%20credible%20and%20urgent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Nepali%20citizens%20themselves%20who%20must%20toil%20to%20keep%20their%20country%20democratic%2C%20inclusive%2C%20stable%20and%20progressing.%20The%20United%20Nations%20can%20assist%2C%20by%20reacquainting%20itself%20with%20Nepal%2C%20its%20foibles%20and%20successes.%20At%20an%20existential%20level%2C%20the%20UN%20needs%20to%20monitor%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20sovereign%20agency%20even%20as%20geopolitical%20alliances%20seek%20to%20foist%20their%20agenda%20on%20Nepal%2C%20and%20the%20anti-minority%20sentiments%20to%20the%20north%20and%20south%20gallop%20threateningly%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20truncated%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98actionable%20matters%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20UN%20Secretary-General%2C%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*Nepal%E2%80%99s%20security%20agencies%20get%C2%A0too%20few%20command%20responsibilities%20in%20UN%20peacekeeping%20operations%20for%20its%20long-standing%20participation%20and%20sizable%20contingent%20in%20a%20dozen%20theaters%20of%20operation.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20where%20the%20good%20offices%20of%20the%20UN%20chief%20would%20be%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*Within%20Nepal%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98clear%20and%20present%20danger%E2%80%99%20that%20bears%20monitoring%20is%20the%20possible%20spread%20of%20%E2%80%98communal%E2%80%99%20wildfires%20from%20the%20Ganga%20plain%20into%20Nepal%2C%20and%20the%20winter-spring%20of%202023-24%20is%20a%20period%20that%20bears%20watching.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*Given%20that%20there%20are%20some%20who%20want%20Nepal%20to%20backslide%20by%20conjuring%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20should%20be%20monitoring%2C%20and%20also%20side%20with%20those%20who%20suggest%20a%20sage%20and%20thorough%20review%20of%20a%20Constitution%20now%20in%20its%20eighth%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*The%20life%20and%20livelihood%20of%20millions%20of%20its%20citizens%20toiling%20as%20labourers%20in%20difficult%20conditions%20in%20India%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20the%20Gulf%20and%20other%20countries%20is%20of%20vital%20concern%20for%20Nepal%2C%20also%20because%20it%20is%20their%20remittance%20that%20is%20helping%20keep%20the%20economy%20afloat.%20Their%20wellbeing%20should%20be%20a%20central%C2%A0part%20of%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20development%20agenda%2C%20to%20be%20understood%20and%20also%20owned%20by%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*Kathmandu%20Valley%2C%20Pokhara%20and%20other%20parts%20should%20be%20utilised%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20for%20its%20international%20conclaves%2C%20given%20the%20open%20visa%20regime%2C%20the%20low%20cost%20of%20hospitality%20services%20and%20good%20air%20connectivity.%20This%20will%20support%20the%20economy%20while%20strengthening%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20positioning%20within%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E*This%20very%20week%2C%20there%20is%20the%20election%20for%20the%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20regional%20head%2C%20with%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh%20competing.%20For%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20two%20billion%20plus%20population%20of%20the%20South-%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20whose%20public%20health%20is%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20office%20in%20question%2C%20the%20Secretary-General%20should%20use%20his%20good%20offices%20to%20ensure%20simply%20that%20the%20more%20qualified%20candidate%20is%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20hopes%20that%20UN%20secretary-general%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%E2%80%99%20visit%20to%20Nepal%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20team%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20Geneva%2C%20New%20York%20and%20elsewhere%20are%20better%20equipped%20to%20observe%20Nepal%20and%20help%20it%20along%20in%20a%20rapidly%20despoiling%20international%20environment.%20But%20one%20might%20ask%20that%20all%20United%20Nations%20cars%20and%20jeeps%20revert%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98regular%E2%80%99%20livery%20from%20before%201996%2C%20rather%20than%20remain%20the%20white%20behemoths%20with%20protruding%20antennae%20and%20%E2%80%98UN%E2%80%99%20written%20in%20big%20blue%20letters.%20These%20ubiquitous%20vehicles%20subconsciously%20remind%20citizens%20that%20the%20conflict%20continues%2C%20whereas%20it%20is%20only%20Transitional%20Justice%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20properly%20brought%20to%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originall