02%20pm%2C%20with%20a%2015-minute%20break%20in%20between.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20lunch%20again%20at%20the%20mess%2C%20Rohan%20rests%20till%203%3A30pm.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20he%20starts%20studying%20in%20three-hour%20stretches.%20He%20takes%20a%20tea%20break%20at%206%3A30pm%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20revision%2C%20and%20then%20has%20his%20dinner%20at%208%3A30pm.%20From%209pm%20to%20midnight%2C%20he%20studies%20again%20before%20going%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%2024%20hours%2C%20Rohan%2C%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%20entrance%20to%20get%20into%20a%20medical%20college%2C%20spends%207%20hours%20in%20class%2C%207.5%20hours%20in%20self-study%2C%20and%20merely%205.5%20hours%20sleeping.%20The%20remaining%20four%20hours%20are%20spent%20travelling%2C%20bathing%20and%20eating.%20He%20hardly%20has%20any%20time%20for%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20routine%20followed%20by%20most%20students%20in%20Kota.%20They%20come%20to%20this%20town%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20coaching%2C%20an%20entrance%20exam%20to%20get%20into%20the%20top%20engineering%20colleges%20in%20India.%20Police%20officials%20of%20the%20city%20state%20that%20almost%2060%20percent%20students%20are%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20being%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20children%20here%2C%20which%20also%20lays%20heavily%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20these%2015-18-year-olds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background.%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20seeing%20the%20other%20students%20here%2C%20who%20are%20equally%20good%2C%20many%20even%20better%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20even%20crack%20the%20exam.%20My%20parents%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20paid%20seat.%20I%