%20or%20older%20at%20home%2C%20these%20male%20and%20female%20officers%20speak%20to%20students%20daily%20in%20an%20informal%20setting.%20They%20are%20part%20of%20the%20special%20student%20cell%20established%20in%20Kota%20on%2024%20June%202023%2C%20which%20has%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20with%20three%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20questions%20like%20is%20anything%20bothering%20them%2C%20do%20they%20really%20want%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20or%20a%20doctor%20or%20if%20they%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20class%20to%20other%20basic%20questions%20like%20do%20they%20like%20the%20food%20being%20served%20in%20the%20mess%2C%20these%20officers%20establish%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20students%20to%20identify%20if%20they%20are%20at%20risk%20or%20if%20they%20are%20doing%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20is%20working%20with%20students%2C%20identifying%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20just%20offering%20a%20listening%20ear%20to%20them.%20We%20look%20for%20red%20flags%20or%20symptoms%20of%20depression%20when%20we%20interact%20with%20students.%20We%20speak%20to%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20mess%20staff%2C%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20understand%20which%20students%20are%20not%20eating%20properly%2C%20who%20is%20returning%20their%20tiffins%20without%20finishing.%20Food%20is%20a%20very%20important%20factor%20for%20these%20children.%20Once%20we%20identify%20these%20children%2C%20we%20speak%20one%20on%20one%20and%20guide%20them%20to%20counsellors%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cell%20also%20has%20a%20control%20room%20where%20police%20personnel%20are%20assigned%20to%20speak%20to%20callers.%20The%20ASP%20states%20that%20they%20receive%20almost%207%20calls%20everyday%20from%20students%20facing%20mental%20health%20issues.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20received%20over%20500%20serious%20calls%20in%20less%20than%20four%20months%2C%20highlighting%20how%20dire%20the%20situation%20is%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShashi%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20a%20NEET%20coaching%20teacher%2C%20is%20on%20a%20sabbatical%20now%20to%20solely%20focus%20on%20counselling%20students.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20these%20suicides%20are%20an%20indicator%20of%20a%20larger%20mental%20health%20issue%20amongst%20students.%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20issues%20he%20has%20noticed%20are%20born%20broadly%20out%20of%20a%20language%20barrier%2C%20financial%20burden%20and%2For%20a%20lack%20of%20career%20counselling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20a%20girl%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20come%20here%20but%20was%20sent%20as%20some%20relative%20of%20hers%20had%20cracked%20the%20NEET%20after%20coaching%20in%20Kota.%20She%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20financial%20and%20familial%20pressure%20of%20it%20all.%20Coming%20from%20a%20Hindi-medium%20school%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything.%20She%20felt%20awkward%20in%20the%20hostels%20as%20most%20people%20spoke%20in%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20confided%20in%20her%20parents%20about%20her%20inability%20to%20understand%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20and%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20come%20back%2C%20her%20parents%20heard%20none%20of%20it.%20Singh%20says%20that%20her%20parents%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CEither%20clear%20the%20NEET%20or%20we%20will%20marry%20you%20off%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20burden%20on%20girls%20is%20much%20more%20than%20boys%2C%20according%20to%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20rising%20student%20suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoys%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20look%20after%20the%20family%20business%2C%20be%20it%20a%20small%20shop%20or%20a%20farm.%20Girls%20are%20not%20even%20given%20that%20option.%20They%20are%20asked%20to%20clear%20the%20entrance%20or%20threatened%20with%20the%20punishment%20of%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20parents%20must%20tell%20their%20children%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%2C%20and%20to%20let%20them%20choose%20other%20career%20options.%20Telling%20a%20barely%2015-year-old%20child%20that%20one%20exam%20is%20the%20do-all%20of%20their%20life%20leads%20to%20catastrophic%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20child%20will%20try%20and%20reach%20out%20for%20help%20about%20a%20hundred%20times%20before%20they%20take%20that%20step.%20We%20must%20address%20this%20problem%20as%20a%20society%20and%20help%20children%20battle%20depression.%20Everyone%20from%20parents%2C%20teachers%2C%20government%20bodies%20must%20preach%20that%20mental%20health%20is%20as%20important%20as%20physical%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20a%20parent%20or%20teacher%20that%20they%20are%20not%20okay%2C%20one%20must%20address%20it%20immediately%20and%20talk%20to%20them.%20Just%20like%20you%20take%20your%20child%20to%20a%20doctor%20when%20they%20have%20a%20fever%2C%20take%20them%20to%20a%20psychologist%20too%20when%20they%20are%20low%20or%20depressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20student%20spends%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20in%20Kota%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-238x300.jpeg%20238w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-16980